    "An in-house-designed flow cell equipped with a reflectance probe was employed for real-time monitoring of hydrolysis by in-line UV-vis spectroscopy.",
    "The raw data was processed using a sophisticated neural network algorithm, yielding rapid quantification with an impressive processing time of 1.4 ms per spectrum.",
